ivates further\napplications of neural networks for studies of turbulence. We make publicly\navailable all data and software needed to reproduce our results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 May 2019 18:12:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Aug 2019 16:31:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-11"}
