gap. Finally, a generalization to the vector Gaussian channel\ncase is discussed. Simulation results demonstrate the advantage of using the BS\nas relay in enhancing the throughput of the FD cellular network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 May 2019 19:40:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 02:46:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-09"}
