 than ten without\naffecting estimator variance or bias.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 May 2019 12:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 09:18:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-23"}
