 nucleus. More\nglobally, strong nucleus heterogeneities at a scale of a few meters are ruled\nout on 67P small lobe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 May 2019 12:28:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-06"}
